ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.datatype

Class XTN

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractType
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractComposite
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.datatype.XTN
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Composite, Type, Visitable, Serializable

    public class XTN
extends AbstractComposite

    Represents an HL7 XTN (Extended Telecommunication Number) data type. This type consists of the following components:

    • Telephone Number (ST)
    • Telecommunication Use Code (ID)
    • Telecommunication Equipment Type (ID)
    • Email Address (ST)
    • Country Code (NM)
    • Area/City Code (NM)
    • Local Number (NM)
    • Extension (NM)
    • Any Text (ST)
    • Extension Prefix (ST)
    • Speed Dial Code (ST)
    • Unformatted Telephone number (ST)
    See Also:
